    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next great project! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for anyone who loves a full restoration or needs a reliable source for parts. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to bring a classic back to life at a budget-friendly price. It's an honest fixer-upper with plenty of potential for the right hands!",
